title: (x) handwritten Kilimanjaro - Funky Fresh {Trajan}
content:
hey what's up.. I'm trying to identify this handwritten font.   
Any help would be much appreciated.   
thanks..   
 ![kilimanjaro.jpg](http://web.archive.org/web/20050525001257im_/http:/www.typophile.com/forums/messages/83/2906.jpg)
author: alius

comments.content: Judging from the differences between the I's and A's, I'd say it was hand-lettered, not typeset.
Nicely done! I stand corrected, although it does look like someone tweaked the letters in question to give the whole thing a more handcrafted appearance.
